{"tid":1004740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國廣告涉抄襲香港芭蕾舞團海報 竟辯稱「向經典致敬」","createTime":"2019-02-01T16:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T05:41:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0e2f69ce5a7dac07e927df35a6444f25089a9a4e","tid":1004740,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpEaJmHB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpEaJmHB.jpg&h=746775f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpWZjKWi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpWZjKWi.jpg&h=d63dfb82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpnGEYGP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpnGEYGP.jpg&h=c41bd0b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港芭蕾舞團為宣傳2018/19年舞季的演出，拍攝了一系列以「Never Stand Still」的香港特色照片。但近日竟被發現，中國小天鵝洗衣機公司在微博貼出的廣告，其中有三幅照片極其相似，懷疑無錫小天鵝抄襲香港芭蕾舞團的廣告。<br />\n<br />\n香港芭蕾舞團去年由Design Army設計公司創作、Dean Alexander拍攝，推出了一系列在香港特色景點擺出芭蕾舞中優雅舞姿的照片。拍攝概念打破既定對芭蕾舞者「穿著紗裙、踮起腳尖」印象。讓舞者們在星光大道、珍寶海鮮舫、維多利亞港等知名景點，以芭蕾舞姿融入地景中，掀起了當時一陣話題。<br />\n<br />\n不料，據臉書專頁《廣告狂人 Madman Monologue》踢爆，中國品牌無錫小天鵝洗衣機公司，在上月29日微博發布了3張廣告海報，海報中場景、物件極其相似，演員衣著、動作等也完全雷同。<br />\n<br />\n《廣告狂人 Madman Monologue》對此酸說，佩服無錫小天鵝洗衣機硬是將洗衣機賣點切入照片之中，像是演員手中的筷子硬是換成不搭嘎的熨斗；原來照片左手提壺，改為右手提花；原照片兩名男子空中對打的畫面，被用作推銷產品「不纏繞」，但其餘肢體、構圖等皆相像。<br />\n<br />\n事件爆發之後，有眼尖網友識破廣告背景中連煙霧都與原始照片如出一轍，許多照片細節也看出破綻。<br />\n<br />\n無錫小天鵝洗衣機公司則在昨天刪除照片，在微博也貼出致歉信，指出海報稿件由代理公司製作，「本著向經典致敬的初衷，但卻沒有尊重原創」，接著表示已成立專責小組進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2690563\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2690563&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxsgqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=ab1adc3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2690563&h=2be39b3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2690563</a>"},{"pid":"fa9d38955a885571c35cdf14cb5079fe40b33fba","tid":1004740,"uid":191352,"like":3,"dislike":34,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T16:20:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1b12f96c53b590b1edafd5c4f984e7ef6574cf7","tid":1004740,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T16:21:10.000Z","msg":"第一張都算<br />\n第二三張真係敬邊忽?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f6e6108dd80f8c6db2e440f5e794aa3401dd11","tid":1004740,"uid":511,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T16:27:12.000Z","msg":"第一張條女揸住個熨斗想做咩呀？熨返直條仔塊面呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0885d1823c7e2d7ff8e4293673bd404ffabf4bab","tid":1004740,"uid":53811,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T17:01:43.000Z","msg":"中國抄襲進步咗，話係致敬就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f199c897eac11e6c6454c78f6e554d718fb7a0cc","tid":1004740,"uid":202139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa9d38955a885571c35cdf14cb5079fe40b33fba","tid":1004740,"uid":191352,"like":3,"dislike":34,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T16:20:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T01:28:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkballet.com/tc/About-Us/Artistic-Members-And-Dancers.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkballet.com%2Ftc%2FAbout-Us%2FArtistic-Members-And-Dancers.html&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxsgqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=40f3f17b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkballet.com/tc/About-Us/Artistic-Members-And-Dancers.html</a><br />\n太少香港舞蹈員"},{"pid":"ea7b88ffc04ed7fd879f6ce9537991f61eca